---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use | ABOH LEGAL"
  description="Terms of Use for the ABOH LEGAL website."
>
  <Hero label="Legal" title="Terms of Use" />

  <section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-10">

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">By accessing this website, you agree to these terms.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">2. Information Only</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">The content on this website is for general information purposes only. It does not constitute legal advice and should not be relied upon as such. Every legal situation is unique, and you should consult directly with a qualified lawyer about your specific circumstances.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">3. No Solicitor-Client Relationship</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">Using this website, sending a message through the contact form, or communicating with ABOH LEGAL through this website does not create a solicitor-client relationship. A solicitor-client relationship is only established through a formal retainer agreement signed by both parties.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">4. Accuracy of Information</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">While we strive to keep the information on this website current and accurate, we make no representations or warranties about the completeness, accuracy, or reliability of any information. Laws and regulations change, and the information on this website may not reflect the most current legal developments.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and images, is the property of ABOH LEGAL and is protected by Canadian copyright law. You may not reproduce, distribute, or use any content without prior written permission.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">6. External Links</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">This website may contain links to third-party websites. ABOH LEGAL is not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">ABOH LEGAL shall not be liable for any damages arising from the use of or inability to use this website or its content.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">8. Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">These terms are governed by the laws of the Province of Alberta and the federal laws of Canada applicable therein.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of modified terms.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">Questions about these terms may be directed to <a href="mailto:info@abohlegal.ca" class="text-gold hover:underline">info@abohlegal.ca</a> or <a href="tel:+18254610107" class="text-gold hover:underline">(825) 461-0107</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
